+{"id":"frankenredis-3jrv","title":"rv89 part 4: OBJECT ENCODING listpack_ex + keyspace events + RDB types 20-23 (fr-store/fr-persist/fr-runtime)","description":"Final slice of br-frankenredis-rv89:\n\n- OBJECT ENCODING reports listpack_ex / hashtable_ex when any per-field TTL is present in a hash.\n- Keyspace events: hexpire, hpexpire, hexpireat, hpexpireat, hpersist, hexpired (on lazy delete).\n- DEBUG OBJECT exposes expired_fields counter.\n- AOF: new inline propagation forms for HEXPIRE/HPEXPIRE/HPERSIST so AOF replay reconstructs field TTLs.\n- RDB: upstream 7.4 types 20 (hashtable_metadata_pre_ga), 21 (hashtable_metadata), 22 (listpack_ex_pre_ga), 23 (listpack_ex) in fr-persist::rdb::decode + encode.\n- Unit tests per axis; round-trip golden tests for RDB + AOF.\n\nLargest remaining scope — can be split further if needed.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-04-23T22:58:07.261536393Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-23T23:33:55.206753001Z","closed_at":"2026-04-23T23:33:55.204754930Z","close_reason":"Closed as an umbrella bead — actual work fanned out into leaf sub-beads: frankenredis-omff (OBJECT ENCODING listpack_ex/hashtable_ex + hexpired keyspace event, f462d78), frankenredis-7jhg (HEXPIRE/HPEXPIRE/HEXPIREAT/HPEXPIREAT/HPERSIST keyspace events, a021a21), frankenredis-t2nh (HGETEX + HGETDEL, 67bf107), frankenredis-25re (DEBUG OBJECT hexpired_fields counter, 29d0229), frankenredis-th7q (RDB types 20-23 — still open, separate format-rewrite scope).","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"frankenredis-3jrv","depends_on_id":"frankenredis-c0z9","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-23T22:58:07.261536393Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
