+{"id":"frankenredis-9jl4","title":"v8s5 part a: document upstream DUMP/RESTORE payload format (fr-store reference)","description":"Preparation sub-bead for br-frankenredis-v8s5. Extract the upstream DUMP payload layout from legacy_redis_code/redis/src/cluster.c::dumpCommand + rdb.c::rdbSaveObject + restoreCommand + rdb.c::rdbLoadObject and write it up as crates/fr-store/docs/dump-format.md.\n\nScope:\n  * Overall payload: type_byte + rdbSaveObject + version (u16 LE) + CRC64 (u64 LE).\n  * Version field semantics (currently upstream is version 11 for 7.2.x, 12 for 7.4.x).\n  * Per-type rdbSaveObject layout for STRING/LIST_QUICKLIST_2/SET_INTSET/SET_LISTPACK/HASH_LISTPACK/HASH_METADATA/ZSET_LISTPACK/STREAM_LISTPACKS_3.\n  * CRC64 polynomial (Redis CRC64 with the Jones polynomial, already implemented at crates/fr-persist/src/lib.rs:848).\n  * A comparison table: current frankenredis-internal layout vs upstream expectation, field-by-field.\n\nNo code changes.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-04-24T00:17:59.107620059Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-24T00:17:59.107620059Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
