+{"id":"frankenredis-hjub","title":"s5su part c: stream decoder for RDB_TYPE_STREAM_LISTPACKS (15) — entries only","description":"Extend fr-persist::decode_rdb to accept upstream type-15 stream records and reconstruct RdbValue::Stream(entries, watermark, []). No consumer groups yet — blank Vec. Uses the listpack decoder from s5su-b.\n\nScope:\n  * Read radix tree pair count, iterate each (stream-id, listpack) pair.\n  * Decode listpack entries into (ms, seq, fields) tuples.\n  * Populate watermark from stream metadata (last_id).\n  * Leave consumer_groups empty (covered by s5su-d).","status":"in_progress","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-04-24T00:17:58.348959392Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-24T00:21:57.224528035Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
