+{"id":"frankenredis-k2lp","title":"s5su part a: document upstream RDB stream on-disk layout (fr-persist reference)","description":"Preparation sub-bead for br-frankenredis-s5su. Extract the upstream RDB_TYPE_STREAM_LISTPACKS (15), _LISTPACKS_2 (19), and _LISTPACKS_3 (21) on-disk layouts from legacy_redis_code/redis/src/rdb.c + t_stream.c and write them up as a reference doc at crates/fr-persist/docs/rdb-stream-format.md.\n\nScope:\n  * Radix tree layout: (stream-id, listpack) pair count + per-pair listpack blob encoding.\n  * Stream metadata fields: length, last_id, first_id, max_deleted_id, entries_added.\n  * Per-group PEL layout: group-name length + name + last-delivered id + pel count + consumer slot.\n  * Per-consumer fields: name + seen_time (v2+) + active_time (v3+) + per-consumer PEL ids.\n  * Field-by-field u64/u32/length-encoded type list so the encoder sub-bead (s5su-d) can be written from this doc alone.\n\nNo code changes.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-04-24T00:17:24.003737528Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-04-24T00:17:24.003737528Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
